    <abstract>
      <t>This document describes requirements, architecture and solutions for MPLS-TP Shared Ring Protection (MSRP) in the ring topology for point- to-point (P2P) services. The mechanism of MSRP is illustrated and how it satisfies the requirements in RFC 5654 for optimized ring protection is analyzed.</t>
